transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan, Vikas ji, Namaskar sir. 
Customer: Haan ji. Namaskar. 
Executive: Sir keh raha hu, Praveen bol raha hu IndiaMART se. 
Customer: Haan ji. 
Executive: Sir Praveen bol raha hu IndiaMART se. 
Customer: Haan Praveen ji. 
Executive: Keh raha hu ye not bag aur polypropelin bag wala out of stock hai kya abhi product? 
Customer: Nahi nahi out of stock kyu ye to running chal raha hai. 
Executive: Running me hai na dono not bag aur polypropelin bag. 
Customer: Haan haan. 
Executive: Achcha. Sir factory pe ho kya aap abhi? 
Customer: Pahuchunga abhi. 
Executive: Pahuching hai. Thoda sa sir wahi catalog ke liye ek bar baat karni thi ek bar update karwa dijiye. 
Customer: Ek bar madam se kar lo na aap. 
Executive: Madam ko lagaya tha mam uthai nahi. 
Customer: Achcha. Aage honge. 
Executive: Office aage baat karo ek bar aap kya baat hai. 
Customer: Haan thoda bol dijiye connect kar lenge to mai karwa deta hu. 
Customer: Thik hai thik hai thik hai. 
Executive: Ho gaya.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants to update the catalog.

- Customer says madam did not pick up.



Resolution:

- Executive asked to call the office.

- Executive will connect to get it done.



Next Steps: 

- None



Alert (If Any):

None
